" Mapping keys:
 
"map <C-b> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
 
" Allows to move current line to Up/Down line using Shift + Arrou Up/Down
nnoremap <S-Up> :m-2<CR>
nnoremap <S-Down> :m+<CR>
inoremap <S-Up> <Esc>:m-2<CR>
inoremap <S-Down> <Esc>:m+<CR>
 
" The same but using j and k
nnoremap <S-k> :m-2<CR>
nnoremap <S-j> :m+<CR>
"inoremap <S-k> <Esc>:m-2<CR>
"inoremap <S-j> <Esc>:m+<CR>

" List all maps
map <C-m> :echom "Normal mode mappings:" <bar> :nmap <CR>

